optionTax.text.1 = This means that the business chose to charge VAT on any income it earns from renting or selling its commercial property.
optionTax.text.2 = Commercial property is usually exempt from VAT. Some businesses choose to charge VAT so they can recover costs, such as from construction and repairs.

